<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Flip Developer Portal</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Submit your extensions to the Flip Browser Marketplace. Build, submit, and publish extensions for thousands of users.">
  <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="/public/fliplogo.png">
  <meta property="og:type" content="website">
  <meta property="og:title" content="Flip Developer Portal">
  <meta property="og:description" content="Submit your extensions to the Flip Browser Marketplace.">
  <meta property="og:image" content="/public/fliplogo.png">
  <meta name="twitter:card" content="summary">
  <meta name="twitter:title" content="Flip Developer Portal">
  <meta name="twitter:description" content="Submit your extensions to the Flip Browser Marketplace.">
  <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
  <script>
    tailwind.config = {
      theme: { extend: { colors: { flip: { 400: '#FB923C', 500: '#F97316', 600: '#EA580C' } } } }
    }
  </script>
</head>
<body class="min-h-screen bg-[#0a0a0f] flex items-center justify-center">
  <div class="text-center mx-4 max-w-lg">
    <img src="/public/fliplogo.png" alt="Flip Browser" class="w-20 h-20 rounded-3xl mx-auto mb-6 shadow-2xl shadow-orange-500/30">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white/90 mb-3">Flip Developer Portal</h1>
    <p class="text-white/40 mb-8 leading-relaxed">Build extensions for Flip Browser and reach thousands of users. Submit your extension for review and get listed on the marketplace.</p>

    <div class="flex flex-col gap-3 max-w-xs mx-auto mb-12">
      <a href="/submit"
        class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-3 px-8 py-4 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-r from-flip-500 to-orange-600 text-white font-semibold text-base hover:opacity-90 transition-opacity shadow-2xl shadow-orange-500/30">
        <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M21 15v4a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-4"/><polyline points="17 8 12 3 7 8"/><line x1="12" y1="3" x2="12" y2="15"/></svg>
        Submit an Extension
      </a>
      <a href="/docs"
        class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 px-8 py-3 rounded-2xl bg-white/[0.04] border border-white/[0.08] text-white/50 font-medium text-sm hover:text-white/70 hover:bg-white/[0.06] transition-colors">
        <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M4 19.5v-15A2.5 2.5 0 0 1 6.5 2H20v20H6.5a2.5 2.5 0 0 1 0-5H20"/></svg>
        Read the Docs
      </a>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-4 text-left mb-12">
      <div class="bg-white/[0.03] border border-white/[0.06] rounded-2xl p-5">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-flip-500/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-3">
          <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="rgba(249,115,22,0.8)" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M14.7 6.3a1 1 0 0 0 0 1.4l1.6 1.6a1 1 0 0 0 1.4 0l3.77-3.77a6 6 0 0 1-7.94 7.94l-6.91 6.91a2.12 2.12 0 0 1-3-3l6.91-6.91a6 6 0 0 1 7.94-7.94l-3.76 3.76z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-white/70 mb-1">Build</h3>
        <p class="text-xs text-white/30 leading-relaxed">Use React JSX, Flip SDK APIs, and the permissions system to build powerful extensions.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white/[0.03] border border-white/[0.06] rounded-2xl p-5">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-flip-500/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-3">
          <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="rgba(249,115,22,0.8)" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M21 15v4a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-4"/><polyline points="17 8 12 3 7 8"/><line x1="12" y1="3" x2="12" y2="15"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-white/70 mb-1">Submit</h3>
        <p class="text-xs text-white/30 leading-relaxed">Upload your .zip package with manifest.json. We validate permissions and security automatically.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white/[0.03] border border-white/[0.06] rounded-2xl p-5">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-flip-500/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-3">
          <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="rgba(249,115,22,0.8)" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"/><polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-white/70 mb-1">Publish</h3>
        <p class="text-xs text-white/30 leading-relaxed">After review, your extension goes live on the Flip Marketplace for all users to install.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <a href="https://croak.work" target="_blank" class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 text-[10px] text-white/15 hover:text-white/30 transition-colors">
      <img src="/public/fliplogo.png" alt="" class="w-3.5 h-3.5 rounded opacity-40">
      CROAKWORKS
    </a>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
